
  To perform transportation duties as deployed by the Supervisor and carry out the duties diligently as per instructions given
  Loading and unloading of goods   
  Reviewing orders before and after delivery to ensure that items are accurate   
  Responsible for proper care and maintenance of the vehicle
  To perform other ad-hoc duties as per assigned by Supervisor


Job Requirements

  Possess Class 4/5 Driving Licence
  Preferably 1 Year Experience in driving tipper truck
  Familiar with Singapore Roads
